    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高通、微软借助人工智能推动个人电脑市场复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/qualcomm-microsoft-lean-on-ai-hype-to-spur-pc-market-revival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从微软公司到高通公司的科技公司正在大力推广一种新型计算机，他们称之为“AI PC”，承诺将在他们的笔记本电脑和台式机中嵌入人工智能功能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/qualcomm-microsoft-lean-on-ai-hype-to-spur-pc-market-revival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
